the marathon family ( serbo-croatian : maratonci trče počasni krug , lit . marathon runners do a lap of honour , or often simply maratonci , lit . the marathon runners ) is a 1982 yugoslav black comedy film written by dušan kovačević and directed by serbian director slobodan šijan .   it has become a cult film in serbia and other countries from the former yugoslavia region and is regarded as one of the classics of yugoslav serbian cinematography .